<p><a href="https://snailedit.dev">Snailed It Development</a>, a clever development team including my friend and former Automators co-host Rosemary Orchard, just released <a href="https://capsuletracker.com">their bespoke medication tracking app, Capsule.</a> It’s got Rose’s fingerprints all over it with multiple options and automations. Definitely worth checking out.</p>
